public interface Transformation
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Transformation'.

The following features are supported:

  • Name
  • Relations
  • Functions
  • Children
  • No Starts
  • No When
  • No Where
  • No Relations
  • No Top Level Relations
  • No Metamodels
